[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ここで……極夜の錬金党を解散する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "そうか……分かった",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "ま、待って！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "アンチュ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "み、みんなもクリセルダも……お願い、待って！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "わ、私、クリセルダにもみんなにもそばにいてほしい！\nでも重荷にはなりたくない！　だから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "自立して頼れる私になるから、だから一緒にいて！\nそう言いたくて、私……これを",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "これを私に？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "クリセルダが、ここでみんなとお別れしようと\n思うなら、ちゃんと受け入れようって思ったの",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "でもやっぱり嫌！　みんなに一緒にいてほしい！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "錬金党がなくなるなら、私が他に何か\n新しい組織を作って、みんなを誘うから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "私、もっとしっかりするから……\nだからみんな、離れないで……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "アンチュ、ありがとう。\nあなたの気持ち、天に昇るほど嬉しいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "それに……言いたいことを先に言われちゃったわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "……え？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "錬金党はなくなるけれど、みんなは私の大切な友。\nこれからも、友でいてほしいと思っているのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "とはいえ、私たちは元錬金党。\nこの関係に名前はいらないし、強制もしない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "だって、そのほうが――自由でしょ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ワルター",
		"romanized_name": "Walther",
		"model_path_hash": "9038662813217487255",
		"text": "友人の名で私の研究を阻害する愚者には\n事欠きませんでしたしね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2249055519964613397",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ええ。自ら友と名乗り、それを強要する者こそ\n王として遠ざけねばならぬ者です",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "この関係は、わたくしたちの心の中にだけあればいい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ああ。なんだかんだ大切な友人で、仲間だ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "うん……うん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "というわけで、今日は私たちの新たな門出。\n盛大にお祝いしましょう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "待ちくたびれたぜ！\nカフェ「星の繭」特製料理だ。残したら許さねえぞ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ロロナ",
		"romanized_name": "Rorona",
		"model_path_hash": "4482406372396026577",
		"text": "リンデ祭にちなんでクリセルダさんと一緒に作った\nチョコ料理でーす！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6911172049205438765",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あら、すべてチョコ料理ですの？\n見事ですわね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "テス",
		"romanized_name": "Tess",
		"model_path_hash": "7713659418971358664",
		"text": "びっくりした？　した？\nこの反応が見たくて、こっそり準備したからね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1974319971304968741",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "アンチュ",
		"romanized_name": "Antje",
		"model_path_hash": "4505991537255215219",
		"text": "びっくり……した",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3623196163129163432",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "クリセルダ",
		"romanized_name": "Criselda",
		"model_path_hash": "2319149981238984606",
		"text": "ふふ……さあ、召しあがれ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2415369427152481317",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "マクダ",
		"romanized_name": "Magda",
		"model_path_hash": "9031925149745762703",
		"text": "ほら。だから言ったろう？　野暮だってさ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2266739299589054477",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "そのようだな。……少し頭が固くなっていたようだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]